data.description: Fantastic location for You & Your Boat. This Moorings condominium offers a great location (close to amenities area and growing commerce), available dock space (leased separately) and very comfortable living. This beautiful condominium has NE views of the Intracoastal Water Way and the Boatyard. The Moorings has restaurants, community services and wonderful waterfront amenities. This wonderful condominium has granite countertops, wood cabinets, breakfast bar with an open concept. The living room has a northern balcony with gorgeous waterfront views for relaxing and dining. The primary suite is quite spacious with a generous walk-in closet with an attached bathroom. There is also a stackable washer and dryer included. All tiles. No carpet! The building also offers bicycle storage, fitness center, swimming pool, valet parking, garage parking and shops. This gorgeous condominium should not be missed!
